Drogan_Healed: 0 at first, 1 when the herbs have been given to Ayala and 2 when the player enters Drogan's Home with the tower statue (NOTE: at that point we're probably going to need to teleport all PC's into the first floor of Drogan's Home, make Drogan get up and have him initiate dialogue with whomever has the tower statue).

Once Drogan_Healed is set to 1, there will need to be a script in Drogan's heartbeat that sets a global on him called Drogan_Ill to either 0, 1 or 2 randomly each heartbeat.
